# GitHub Language Detection Overrides
# Force the project to prioritize Java in language statistics

# Treat the entire frontend directory as vendored/generated so it doesn't skew language stats
frontend/**/* linguist-vendored

# Ensure Java files are always counted
backend/src/main/java/**/* linguist-detectable
backend/pom.xml linguist-detectable

# Ignore documentation and assets from language stats
README.md linguist-documentation
backend/src/main/resources/templates/**/* linguist-documentation
backend/src/main/resources/static/**/* linguist-documentation
